This directory contains data for building Zabbix RPM packages for
CentOS 5 and RHEL 5 GNU/Linux distributions.

* build.sh
Run this script to generate RPM packages. Make sure rpm Release is
properly set in zabbix.spec.tmpl .

* SOURCES
This directory contains scripts, patches, config files that are
referenced from the spec file.

* zabbix.spec.tmpl
This is the template that is used to generate RPM spec file when you
run build.sh script. Please do not forget to update changelog when
it's changed. Keep the upper most changelog entry the templated
one. When you run build.sh script the template variables will be
replaced with needed values.
